        "System.Description": "<div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\">The csBus Date is returning the date format for transactions as mmddyy instead of mmddyyyy and this is causing the wrong date to transmit to Central Site.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Example:&nbsp;</div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\">03/30/2020 12:15:44 --- Before TCStartEditTran(<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">csBusDate=30200330,</b></div><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Zeus will add code to handle mmddyy when returned.&nbsp;</div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><br></div><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">See attached email for additional details.&nbsp;</div><br></div>",
